Wednesday 5/3: Between 9 – 10am EST and any time after 2:30pm Thursday 5/4: Between 9:30 – 12pm EST and 2 – 3pm Friday 5/5: Between 8 – 10am EST and 11:30am – 2pm Best, James From: Denise James [mailto:denise_james@nwrdc.fsu.edu] Sent: Tuesday, May 2, 2017 1:18 PM To: James Wilcox <james.wilcox@turbonomic.com> Cc: Stephen Ropes <stephen_ropes@nwrdc.fsu.edu> Subject: RE: Turbonomic: Coordinating Next Discussion James,I was out of the office today and I’m going to be patching the environment until Friday afternoon.Not sure how this will affect the testing lots of migrations will be taking place.I haven’t looked at the calendar yet since I was out of the office on Friday.Sorry about the delay but I will get back with you by COB tomorrow. We may have to push this to next week since I’m patching. Denise O.
